<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="User_interface">User interface</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Pascal%27s_calculator&amp;action=edit&amp;section=11" title="Edit section: User interface">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
